name: LIFE IS FULL OF POSSIBILITIES
description:
46 pages
Black and white book, 4-color covers, with black and white interior text and photos printed on 60-pound cream-colored text paper.
Signed by the artist.


LIFE IS FULL OF POSSIBILITIES is an ever expanding and changing collection of images taken from my daily life, and has been realized and displayed in many different formats.  This just one example.
